{"tid":136964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴將續約雲格2年 廠迷還能忍？","createTime":"2017-02-27T12:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T01:10:48.000Z","uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd3b3436e27aa79e7b15db8dbfeb429965ec8f9","tid":136964,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"歐冠盃慘敗瀕臨出局、英超又爭冠無望，阿仙奴無疑又將迎來一個失敗的賽季。年復一年重覆的劇情，也讓球迷對雲格的怒火達到了極限。不過，球迷的怒火，似乎很難影響到雲格的未來，因為阿仙奴高層又一次準備續約雲格了。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格和阿仙奴的合約，到今年夏天就要到期。也因此，雲格的未來，引起了人們的廣泛關注。英國權威媒體《泰晤士報》透露，阿仙奴高層已經將一份為期2年的新合約，擺在了雲格的桌子上，他們只等雲格簽名。在續約一事上，高層給了雲格充分的自主權。不過雲格並未急著簽字，他想要等到今年3月或者4月時再做出決定。<br />\n<br />\n　　雖然雲格遲遲沒有簽字，但人們卻不擔心雲格會拒絕這份新合約。《泰晤士報》透露，阿仙奴球員和員工都深信，雲格將會續約留在阿仙奴。該媒體更是報導，雲格如今甚至已經開始製定阿仙奴今夏的季前備戰計劃，這無疑意味著，雲格心裡已經做出了決定，那就是他依然會留在阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格的未來，而今已經讓阿仙奴球迷分裂。「反雲派」厭倦了球隊年復一年無冠的劇情，他們強烈要求雲格離開阿仙奴。「保雲派」則表示，雲格曾帶給阿仙奴無限輝煌，球隊不該解僱這位功勳教練。可以預計的是，雲格若無法帶領阿仙奴在賸剩餘賽季踢出不錯成績，那屆時反對他留任的聲音，無疑將會更加的猛烈。"},{"pid":"8721d228845b3aa1790d5270529ff4c622248bf4","tid":136964,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/02/27/a/a6459ce07b2a097daa5b580d3053ec1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2Fa%2Fa6459ce07b2a097daa5b580d3053ec1a.jpg&h=39ef0f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0ecad725aad255fba5526bc6b855c1bffa91fc","tid":136964,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"忍住唔喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c047e1ea9981b902b00b1f8e5690eba76574004","tid":136964,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"反雲又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47656821dd65f355699b0bcf5453456cd9807ac","tid":136964,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"永續"},{"pid":"84626e7e4fb9c24ad753049da63a1390142f3821","tid":136964,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"雲加又蠃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d05213c9b859ba279283ce0ea17a7ad1d2116f","tid":136964,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ac07401a19765bab00cdc8f590412a3bbf56fe","tid":136964,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"躝啦死老野"},{"pid":"09d8dab92d3aa7b9b81e85212a5222ac95b7fd8c","tid":136964,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"雲加好波"},{"pid":"abced0a2120123208703308bbdaaf00fb55b694d","tid":136964,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴有雲加真係福氣黎"},{"pid":"3263e0a4d8ed69efcf611a80569c7394639ca482","tid":136964,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"痴線, 續兩年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40c839bce4d83434e2f1e7b55b4aa4c1435bbeb","tid":136964,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>躝啦死老野</blockquote><br />\n唔驚走左好似曼利咁衰幾年？"},{"pid":"568965849ec64395ea6f764851ff61b64025a6ee","tid":136964,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"支持雲加"},{"pid":"c509ecb45c9c76d4da6414f17c072607616d92bc","tid":136964,"uid":9703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"無左雲加，頭四都難，分分鐘跌到中遊"},{"pid":"cd964